ar6-impact:ChangesInFreshwaterEcosystem rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                        rdfs:subClassOf ar6-impact:ChangesInEcosystemStructure .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/crima/ipcc-ar6-impacts#ChangesInOceanEcosystem
ar6-impact:ChangesInOceanEcosystem rdf:type owl:Class ;
