###  http://www.semanticweb.org/crima/ipcc-ar6-impacts#DamagesToKeyEconomicInfrastructures
ar6-impact:DamagesToKeyEconomicInfrastructures rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                               rdfs:subClassOf ar6-impact:ImpactOnCitiesSettlementsInfrastructres .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/crima/ipcc-ar6-impacts#Displacement
ar6-impact:Displacement rdf:type owl:Class ;
                        rdfs:subClassOf ar6-impact:ImpactOnHealthAndWellbeing .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/crima/ipcc-ar6-impacts#FisheriesAndAquacultureProduction
ar6-impact:FisheriesAndAquacultureProduction rdf:type owl:Class ;
