ar6-impact:MentalHealth rdf:type owl:Class ;
                        rdfs:subClassOf ar6-impact:ImpactOnHealthAndWellbeing .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/crima/ipcc-ar6-impacts#ObservedImpacts
ar6-impact:ObservedImpacts rdf:type owl:Class ;
                           rdfs:subClassOf skos:ConceptScheme .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/crima/ipcc-ar6-impacts#OceanEcosystemPhenologyChanges
ar6-impact:OceanEcosystemPhenologyChanges rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                          rdfs:subClassOf ar6-impact:PhenologyChanges .


