ar6-impact:OceanSpeciesShift rdf:type owl:Class ;
                             rdfs:subClassOf ar6-impact:SpeciesRangeShift .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/crima/ipcc-ar6-impacts#PhenologyChanges
ar6-impact:PhenologyChanges rdf:type owl:Class ;
                            rdfs:subClassOf ar6-impact:ImpactOnEcosystems .


