###  http://www.semanticweb.org/crima/crima-ecv#Wind-vertical-InTheBoundaryLayer
ecv:Wind-vertical-InTheBoundaryLayer rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                              ecv:ecv-product ;
